Phase 1 - Mastering Redirections:
First of all, I have read these articles to understand the topic better:
- https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/linux-unix/input-output-redirection-in-linux/;
- https://www.redhat.com/en/blog/linux-shell-redirection-pipelining.
Then I have practiced:
1) ls /etc > files.log
ls /not_real_dir 2> errors.log
cat files.log errors.log;
2) ping -c 3 google.com > ping.log 2>&1;
3) Created the script redirection_test.sh.

